@startuml
title AI Interview Practice Activity Diagram
start
:Candidate opens a job detail page;
:Click "Practice Interview with AI";
:System loads selected job\nand candidate profile context;
:AI generates the first\ninterview question;
:Display question to candidate;

repeat
  :Candidate types response;
  :Frontend sends message history,\njob context, and profile summary;
  :Backend forwards prompt to AI model;

  if (AI returns valid response?) then (Yes)
    :Show feedback on the candidate answer;
    :Display next interview question;
  else (No)
    :Show fallback message\nand allow retry;
  endif

repeat while (Continue practice?) is (Yes)

:End interview practice session;
stop
@enduml
